02:18.847 --> 02:23.601
♪ Looks like the landslide ♪
♪ Is taking me down ♪

02:27.230 --> 02:29.732
TRACE & LEIGH:
♪ Crushin' through my heart ♪

02:29.899 --> 02:32.193
♪ When you come around ♪

02:32.402 --> 02:34.529
- Something to see, isn't it?
- Uh...

02:35.155 --> 02:36.614
Yeah, it's crazy.

02:36.781 --> 02:39.993
Crazy thing is, after a while...

02:40.160 --> 02:42.203
crazy seems normal.

02:42.370 --> 02:43.413
[CROWD CHEERING]

02:43.580 --> 02:49.961
♪ Then the storm comes up ♪
♪ And you flyin' on back to him ♪

02:52.881 --> 02:56.551
♪ Girl, you know it was time ♪
♪ You've gotta cross the line ♪

02:56.718 --> 02:58.553
♪ Just put your hand in mine ♪

02:58.720 --> 03:02.974
♪ 'Cause I'm the only one ♪
♪ Who knows your heart ♪

03:03.141 --> 03:05.018
♪ And when you fall apart ♪

03:05.184 --> 03:09.939
♪ And how to hold you ♪
♪ When you're sad and lonely ♪

03:12.150 --> 03:14.819
♪ Plane ticket already paid ♪

03:15.028 --> 03:17.655
♪ I'm gone ♪
♪ But I don't mean nothing ♪

03:17.822 --> 03:21.367
♪ I'm close even though I'm far away ♪

03:23.703 --> 03:26.289
♪ That's how I remember you ♪

03:26.497 --> 03:29.125
♪ Stuck here on the red-eye special ♪

03:29.292 --> 03:33.004
♪ I can't wait to see you again ♪

03:35.048 --> 03:38.635
♪ So don't think of
me I've been around ♪

03:40.845 --> 03:44.110
♪ Just listen for the
sweet, sweet sound ♪

03:44.111 --> 03:46.851
♪ Of the taxi pulling up the driveway ♪

03:47.018 --> 03:49.395
♪ I'm coming home soon ♪

03:53.149 --> 03:55.526
♪ I'm coming home soon ♪

03:56.527 --> 03:58.655
♪ Doo-da, da-da-da ♪

03:59.197 --> 04:01.532
♪ Da-da-da-da ♪

04:02.367 --> 04:04.744
♪ Doo-da, da-da-da ♪

04:05.578 --> 04:07.455
♪ Da-da-da ♪

04:08.081 --> 04:10.583
♪ Doo-da, da-da-da ♪

04:10.584 --> 04:13.100
